collection.name: CryptoRayRays
collection.description:
Woof woo—oh sorry, hi! My name is RayRay, the goodest vizsla girl from NYC now living in LA. When I’m not coding, I like to wiggle my butt. 

I always wanted a punk, but there weren’t any for dogs like me. This inspired me to design & develop CryptoRayRays - 10,000 unique collectible tokens with proof of ownership stored on the Ethereum blockchain. Your token allows unlimited pets and belly rubs.
